Block trafficSignalSystem
    Block trafficSignal
        Property color : String
        Enumeration green, yellow, red
        State greenState : State
            Initial greenState
            Transition onEntry: (self.color = 'green')
            Transition onExit: (self.color <> 'green')
        State yellowState : State
            Initial yellowState
            Transition onEntry: (self.color = 'yellow')
            Transition onExit: (self.color <> 'yellow')
        State redState : State
            Initial redState
            Transition onEntry: (self.color = 'red')
            Transition onExit: (self.color <> 'red')
        State currentState : State
            Initial currentState
            Transition onEntry: (self.color = (trafficSignal.color))
            Transition onExit: (self.color <> (trafficSignal.color))
    EndBlock

    Block greenLight
        Block greenLightComponent
            Property name : String
            Initial name = 'Green Light'
            Extension trafficSignal
        EndBlock
    EndBlock
EndBlock

Block vehicle
    Property size : Integer (min: 0)

Block engine
    Property vehicle : vehicle (opposite: hasEngine)
    Property numCylinders : Integer (min: 4, max: 6)

Block cylinder
    Property engine : engine (opposite: hasCylinder)

Block smallVehicle
    Extends vehicle

Block largeVehicle
    Extends vehicle

Block standardEngine
    Extends engine
    Operation configure()
        Prepostcondition: self.vehicle.size >= 0
        Postcondition: self.numCylinders = (self.vehicle.size < 5 ? 4 : 6)

Block smallEngine
    Extends engine
    Operation configure()
        Prepostcondition: self.vehicle.size >= 0
        Postcondition: self.numCylinders = 4

Block largeEngine
    Extends engine
    Operation configure()
        Prepostcondition: self.vehicle.size >= 0
        Postcondition: self.numCylinders = 6
